<doc id="1044862" wikidata="Q5116320" url="?curid=1044862" title="Chung Kwei (algorithm)">
<text>Chung Kwei is a spam filtering algorithm based on the TEIRESIAS Algorithm for finding coding genes within bulk DNA. It is named after Zhong Kui, a figure in Chinese folklore.

